description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;We believe in innovation; we believe in listening to everyone; we believe in providing quality service; and we believe our employees will help us achieve our mission.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are seeking a Contract Lead to join the Omnes Healthcare Family; become part of a company that makes a difference.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Salary: £29,000 per annum&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Hours: 40 per week&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Location: Remote and apx 4 days onsite per month (London and Southend)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;em&gt;We have fully COVID compliant infection control policies in place&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who we are:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Omnes Healthcare are a trusted partner in delivering primary and secondary NHS care services. Our quality services cover a wide range of specialities, including General Practice, and our aim is to provide accessible and patient-focused care by working collaboratively and embracing new ways of working, including the application of innovative technology.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are dedicated to achieving better outcomes for our patients, whilst supporting the NHS and saving our commissioners money.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our staff are rewarded by becoming an integral part of delivering excellent patient care, working within a growing company and our attractive employee benefits, including remote working and your birthday off! Join an expanding organisation and take advantage of a brand-new employer in your area!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What is the purpose of the position?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;As a Contract Lead, you will be reporting to the Deputy and Director of the Healthcare Operations Centre and will be managing a team of Patient Healthcare Advisors and Team Leaders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The Contract Lead will oversee and be responsible for the performance and the delivery of excellent customer service for their service portfolios.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What are the key responsibilities?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will be responsible for a team, whilst also managing and maintaining the contractual and company KPI&#39;s&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will be required to liaise with other Management, and other levels, to ensure the smooth running of their services&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will be required to work closely with several Clients, Commissioning Groups, Service Managers and other patient facing teams to continuously develop and improve the services that we provide&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What do you need to join the Omnes Healthcare Family?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Team management experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clear thinking and have an analytical approach&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to work as part of a team, to promote a good team spirit and to be sensitive and assertive as appropriate&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience of personnel issues including recruitment, training and supervision&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to lead a team remotely&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work remotely with suitable broadband connection&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to attend our Head Office at London Bridge (Southend Onwards from Dec 2020) and | or GP and Secondary Care Practices as required to attend training sessions, participate in engagement activities and other duties when required.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What Omnes Healthcare will offer you in return?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A great place to work and the opportunity to make a difference&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;25 days holiday plus bank holidays&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An extra day off to celebrate your birthday&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;NHS Discount&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Remote working capabilities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;And other fantastic benefits&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Apply today if you would like to make a difference.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Please be aware that all communications about this vacancy will be received to you via email. Always check your mailbox and junk mail folders and provide a UK mobile number if available.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
